## Verification Checklist

- [ ] `gblockparty deploy` requires authentication and a linked project
- [ ] Git branch is auto-detected from the current repository
- [ ] Git commit SHA is auto-detected from HEAD
- [ ] `--branch` overrides the detected branch
- [ ] `--prod` triggers a production deployment
- [ ] Default (no `--prod`) triggers a preview deployment
- [ ] `POST /api/cli/deploy` is called with correct payload
- [ ] Build logs stream in real-time in the terminal
- [ ] ANSI colors are preserved in log output
- [ ] Success message includes the deployment URL
- [ ] Failure message includes the error details
- [ ] Build log streaming interruption is handled gracefully
- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes
